title: Woo Shop Slider 1.2.3 - WooCommerce Slider
description: Visit us on: https://www.nulledforums.org Create amazing content with one of our 8 totally different WooCommerce slider styles. You can easily place featured products in a cool responsive slider and let your visitors fully experience what you have to offer. Sliders generate a shortcode which means that they can be placed anywhere on your website and they will fit right into the content. We have also created a Visual Composer shortcode, so if you have both Visual Composer and Free Woo Shop Slider WordPress Plugin you can easily add new sliders to your content. Woo Shop Slider WordPress Plugin Features 8 Different Sliders in 1 Lazy Loading Visual Composer Friendly Quick View Responsive Design Swipe Functionality
